<DOCNO> LA060694-0140 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 048888 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 6, 1994, Monday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
