<TEXT>
<P>
 A 16-year-old girl was struck and killed by a train late Saturday in what 
coroners' investigators said was the third apparent suicide on Orange County 
railroad tracks in the past four weeks. 
</P>
<P>
 Cecilia Pacheco of Anaheim walked in front of an Orange County Metrolink train 
near South Cypress Street in Anaheim about 9 p.m., authorities said Sunday. 
