<TEXT>
<P>
 LEARN: In the graphic on the reform program Los Angeles for Educational 
Alliance for Restructuring Now that ran Monday, May 30, the locations of 
Carthay Center Elementary School and Bryson Avenue Elementary School were 
incorrect. Carthay Elementary is in the Wilshire area of Los Angeles and Bryson 
Elementary is in the Southgate area. 
</P>
